title: Emerica Presents: The Hsu G6
description:
Emerica is proud to announce the release of Jerry Hsu’s new pro model shoe, the Hsu G6; a remastered classic with a redesigned lightweight build: http://emerica.com/shoes/the-hsu-g6/black-white/

“I wanted a clean light weight shoe that protected me. I really love my first shoe, so to evolve from there was the only way I wanted to go.” - Jerry

And that’s what Jerry got.

This is the lightest Vulc Mid on the market and with the newly developed Internal Cage, the Hsu G6 won’t bag out. Available now at #HigherQuality skate shops everywhere.
